Community app wireframe


Front page

  -index, show community posts
  -link to create form
  


Subcommunity
  
  -controller
  -model
    -name
    

  -associations
    -user
    -subscribed

  -Post
    -comments
      -associations
        -post
        -user
        

  -show page for each subcommunity
    -create new post

    -show page for each post
      -create comment 


User features
  -log in
  -reg
  -forgot pw
  -profile show page
    -all comments

  


